snippet.title: Need for Speed Most Wanted (2012) Ps Vita Gameplay
snippet.description:
All footage was captured from original hardware.
This is a good game and definitely one to own if you have a Vita, it's the full game and it runs quite well with a only a few stutters and the music skips now and again but if you like your graphics go for the console or pc version.

PC Gameplay: https://youtu.be/TV5XN3Y2nnU
